import pandas as pd
df=inputs[0]

df0=df.iloc[:,-1]
df0=df0/12

df1=df.iloc[:,:8]
df = pd.concat([df1,df0],axis=1)

df['기준년월']=df['기준년월'].apply(lambda x: (x[:4]+'-'+x[4:6]+'-'+x[6:]))
df['기준년월']=pd.to_datetime(df['기준년월'])
df = df.sort_values(['기준년월','성별','연령별','직업구분','분위구분'], ascending = True)
df['기준년월']=df['기준년월'].astype(str)
